1
00:01:07,439 --> 00:01:09,560
Still won't persuade him to go to Lyon?

2
00:01:12,359 --> 00:01:13,159
Persuade him?

3
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:16,400
The most important thing in our field

4
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:18,079
is respecting the patient's chief complaint.

5
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:22,319
If he wants to stay, he has his reasons.

6
00:01:24,319 --> 00:01:25,959
Ten years ago, very few hospitals here

7
00:01:26,040 --> 00:01:28,719
could do complex dental implant surgery.

8
00:01:29,319 --> 00:01:31,040
And imported materials cost a fortune.

9
00:01:31,799 --> 00:01:32,799
But now?

10
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:34,359
Materials are produced domestically.

11
00:01:34,599 --> 00:01:35,799
Prices have come down.

12
00:01:36,239 --> 00:01:38,359
People can afford dental care now.

13
00:01:38,799 --> 00:01:41,319
Watching Jiang Tiancai face those patients

14
00:01:41,439 --> 00:01:42,599
with that sincere smile,

15
00:01:43,319 --> 00:01:45,840
isn't that more meaningful than

16
00:01:46,359 --> 00:01:47,359
receiving an invitation from Lyon?

17
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:50,359
No matter what you say,

18
00:01:50,879 --> 00:01:51,959
I won't give up.

19
00:01:54,959 --> 00:01:56,280
I've loved him for fifteen years.

20
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,719
Even if the two of you get together,

21
00:01:59,239 --> 00:02:00,599
I won't just sit back and accept it.

22
00:02:04,359 --> 00:02:05,519
Actually, every single paper of yours

23
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:07,519
on postoperative analgesia optimization,

24
00:02:08,159 --> 00:02:09,319
I've read several times.

25
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:10,520
I kept wondering,

26
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:12,439
how do you manage to deliver anesthesia

27
00:02:12,599 --> 00:02:13,759
with such precision?

28
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:16,120
An anesthesiologist who can keep patients

29
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,800
fully conscious and pain-free in surgery,

30
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,840
for us in oral surgery,

31
00:02:19,919 --> 00:02:21,319
is nothing short of a guardian angel.

32
00:02:22,439 --> 00:02:23,520
There's no need to flatter me.

33
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:24,199
No, no, no.

34
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,199
I'm not flattering you at all.

35
00:02:25,439 --> 00:02:26,479
I often think,

36
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:29,479
if I could use the latest technology to

37
00:02:29,599 --> 00:02:32,159
help a kid with Congenital tooth agenesis,

38
00:02:32,319 --> 00:02:34,280
restore their confidence and their smile,

39
00:02:34,719 --> 00:02:37,000
so they stop hiding their smiles in shame,

40
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:40,319
then I'd feel truly proud of myself.

41
00:02:46,759 --> 00:02:48,520
I hope we can both become

42
00:02:48,639 --> 00:02:49,639
the brightest light

43
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:51,919
in our own fields.

44
00:02:55,759 --> 00:02:56,439
Take care,

45
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:57,479
Dr. Lin.

46
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:28,400
As you wish.

47
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,800
Satisfied now?

48
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,960
Chen Pei'ang just left,

49
00:03:38,199 --> 00:03:39,960
and you couldn't wait to promote me.

50
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:42,080
You're throwing me into the fire.

51
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,439
How am I supposed to face anyone?

52
00:03:44,159 --> 00:03:44,960
You little rascal.

53
00:03:45,319 --> 00:03:46,719
Stop acting like you're the victim here.

54
00:03:47,599 --> 00:03:48,759
You think I don't know?

55
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,319
That training opportunity in Lyon,

56
00:03:50,919 --> 00:03:52,479
you gave it up for Dr. Chen.

57
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:58,599
Why the General Dentistry Department?

58
00:03:59,439 --> 00:04:00,520
Maxillofacial Surgery,

59
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,159
or it's off the table.

60
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:03,960
Young man,

61
00:04:04,879 --> 00:04:06,360
don't mistake the platform for ability.

62
00:04:06,719 --> 00:04:07,639
Talented people

63
00:04:08,159 --> 00:04:09,520
shine wherever they go.

64
00:04:15,159 --> 00:04:16,279
To recognize and correct one's mistakes

65
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:17,920
is the greatest virtue, after all.

66
00:04:18,199 --> 00:04:19,360
After all, in his field,

67
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,920
