68
00:04:22,279 --> 00:04:24,040
So you're that sure

69
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,439
that after he comes back,

70
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:27,319
he won't fight you tooth and nail again?

71
00:04:30,959 --> 00:04:32,079
I choose to believe

72
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:34,959
in the power of belief.

73
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,040
Dr. Jiang,

74
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:50,279
your follow-up patient is here.

75
00:05:00,439 --> 00:05:01,959
Go on then. I'll look around.

76
00:05:02,079 --> 00:05:02,920
Okay.

77
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,920
Come on, let big brother take a listen.

78
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:19,920
It's okay.

79
00:05:20,639 --> 00:05:21,800
There's just

80
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,279
a little bug in your tummy.

81
00:05:23,519 --> 00:05:25,279
I'll help you get rid of it. Let's go.

82
00:06:07,079 --> 00:06:08,279
Hey, Jiang Tiancai.

83
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:10,040
It was just a simple oral examination.

84
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,959
Why did you make it hurt so much?

85
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,800
This wisdom tooth of yours,

86
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,480
is just like you,

87
00:06:16,759 --> 00:06:19,160
