90
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:28,040
Your skills are clearly just subpar.

91
00:06:28,759 --> 00:06:29,879
Don't go around saying that.

92
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,160
If anyone hears,

93
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:33,480
