94
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:36,079
Then give me some hush money.

95
00:06:46,879 --> 00:06:48,839
Use an ice pack for tooth pain.

96
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,560
Jiang Tiancai!

97
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:52,319
The rate of oral diseases in our country

98
00:06:52,519 --> 00:06:53,360
is rising year by year,

99
00:06:54,199 --> 00:06:56,079
and affecting younger people.

100
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,720
What does this mean?

101
00:06:58,279 --> 00:07:00,120
It means our task as dentists

102
00:07:00,319 --> 00:07:01,319
is getting increasingly difficult,

103
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,120
and our responsibility ever greater.

104
00:07:03,319 --> 00:07:05,240
We must not only improve clinical skills,

105
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:07,839
but also promote oral health awareness.

106
00:07:07,879 --> 00:07:08,519
Qi Yue.

107
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:10,279
Really going to the Prevention Center?

108
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:12,079
The work there isn't easier than here.

109
00:07:13,079 --> 00:07:15,439
I feel public education really suits me.

110
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:16,680
I'm definitely going.

111
