130
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:07,240
A true protégé of Director Zeng.

131
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:09,600
The student has surpassed the master.

132
00:08:09,959 --> 00:08:10,839
But I think,

133
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:13,160
Precise and powerful as this machine is,

134
